
---

### **5. `.gitignore` (Git Ignore File)**

This file specifies files and directories to ignore in version control.

```gitignore
# Node.js
node_modules/
npm-debug.log

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.db
*.sqlite3
.env
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Docker
.env
docker-compose.override.yml

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# Logs
logs/
*.log

# Build files
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/